import React, {useState} from "react";
import Button from 'react-bootstrap/Button';
import Modal from 'react-bootstrap/Modal';
import Row from 'react-bootstrap/Row';
import Col from 'react-bootstrap/Col';
import { Form } from "react-bootstrap";
import CheckIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Check';

function CreateModal() {

  function submitInfo() {
    <CreateModalCount />
  }
  
  return (
    <Modal
      {...props}
      size="lg"
      aria-labelledby="contained-modal-title-vcenter"
      centered
    >
      <Modal.Header closeButton>
        <Modal.Title id="contained-modal-title-vcenter">
          New Combination
        </Modal.Title>
      </Modal.Header>
      <Modal.Body>
      <Form> 
      <Row >
        <Col>
          <Form.Select aria-label="Category">
            <option>Combination Category</option>
            <option value="1">Tendue from First</option>
            <option value="2">Tendue from Fifth</option>
            <option value="3">Degage</option>
          </Form.Select>
        </Col>
        <Col>
          <Form.Select aria-label="tyle">
            <option>Count Style</option>
            <option value="Count">Count</option>
            <option value="And">And</option>
            <option value="And A">And A</option>
          </Form.Select>
        </Col>
      </Row>
      <Row>
        <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="formBasicEmail">
          <Form.Control 
          placeholder="Combination Name" 
          name="title"
          />
        </Form.Group>

      </Row>
      <Row>
        <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="formBasicEmail">
          <Form.Control 
          placeholder="Notes" 
          name="notes"
          />
        </Form.Group>
      </Row>
      </Form>
      </Modal.Body>

      <Modal.Footer>
        <Button variant="light" onClick={submitInfo}><CheckIcon /></Button>
      </Modal.Footer>

    </Modal>
  );
}

export default CreateModal
